What if the secret to living longer and feeling happier has nothing to do with diet, exercise, or career success?

According to The Harvard Study of Adult Development‚Äîthe longest-running happiness research ever conducted‚Äîit all comes down to relationships. Grab your phone. Text someone. Set up that lunch. The calendar isn't going to clear itself, and the people who matter most won't wait forever.
